ercati predittivi. Le commissioni giornaliere per le transazioni hanno raggiunto ",{"type":23,"tag":28,"props":220,"children":221},{},[222],{"type":32,"value":223},"$1.8 milioni",{"type":32,"value":225}," la settimana scorsa, il 45% in più rispetto al mese precedente.",{"type":23,"tag":51,"props":227,"children":229},{"id":228},"situazione-competitiva",[230],{"type":23,"tag":56,"props":231,"children":233},{"href":232},"#situazione-competitiva",[234],{"type":32,"value":235},"Situazione competitiva",{"type":23,"tag":24,"props":237,"children":238},{},[239],{"type":32,"value":240},"Mentre Arbitrum cresce, altre soluzioni Layer 2 affrontano delle sfide:",{"type":23,"tag":90,"props":242,"children":243},{},[244,254,264],{"type":23,"tag":94,"props":245,"children":246},{},[247,252],{"type":23,"tag":28,"props":248,"children":249},{},[250],{"type":32,"value":251},"Optimism",{"type":32,"value":253}," resta al livello di $1.1 miliardi di TVL",{"type":23,"tag":94,"props":255,"children":256},{},[257,262],{"type":23,"tag":28,"props":258,"children":259},{},[260],{"type":32,"value":261},"Polygon zkEVM",{"type":32,"value":263}," ha soltanto $85 milioni",{"type":23,"tag":94,"props":265,"children":266},{},[267,272],{"type":23,"tag":28,"props":268,"children":269},{},[270],{"type":32,"value":271},"Base",{"type":32,"value":273}," mantiene $1.4 miliardi, ma con maggiore volatilità",{"type":23,"tag":51,"props":275,"children":277},{"id":276},"impatto-sul-token-arb",[278],{"type":23,"tag":56,"props":279,"children":281},{"href":280},"#impatto-sul-token-arb",[282],{"type":32,"value":283},"Impatto sul token ARB",{"type":23,"tag":24,"props":285,"children":286},{},[287,289,294,296,301],{"type":32,"value":288},"La crescita del TVL ha influito positivamente sul token ",{"type":23,"tag":28,"props":290,"children":291},{},[292],{"type":32,"value":293},"ARB",{"type":32,"value":295},", che è salito del ",{"type":23,"tag":28,"props":297,"children":298},{},[299],{"type":32,"value":300},"18%",{"type":32,"value":302}," in una settimana. Tuttavia, gli analisti osservano che l'utilità del token rimane prevalentemente di governance.",{"type":23,"tag":51,"props":304,"children":306},{"id":305},"prospettive",[307],{"type":23,"tag":56,"props":308,"children":310},{"href":309},"#prospettive",[311],{"type":32,"value":312},"Prospettive",{"type":23,"tag":24,"props":314,"children":315},{},[316,318,323],{"type":32,"value":317},"La sostenibilità della crescita dipenderà dalla capacità di Arbitrum di mantenere il vantaggio tecnologico e di continuare ad attrarre capitale istituzionale. Il prossimo aggiornamento ",{"type":23,"tag":28,"props":319,"children":320},{},[321],{"type":32,"value":322},"Ethereum Dencun",{"type":32,"value":324}," potrebbe ridurre ulteriormente il costo delle transazioni L2, intensificando la concorrenza.",{"title":7,"searchDepth":326,"depth":326,"links":327},2,[328,329,333,334,335,336,337],{"id":53,"depth":326,"text":61},{"id":76,"depth":326,"text":83,"children":330},[331],{"id":135,"depth":332,"text":142},3,{"id":164,"depth":326,"text":171},{"id":193,"depth":326,"text":200},{"id":228,"depth":326,"text":235},{"id":276,"depth":326,"text":283},{"id":305,"depth":326,"text":312},"markdown","content:crypto:post_q3phzbrt-it.md","content","crypto\u002Fpost_q3phzbrt-it.md","crypto\u002Fpost_q3phzbrt-it","md",null,[346,354,360],{"_path":347,"title":348,"lead":349,"rubric":5,"author":350,"date":351,"cover":352,"readingTime":353},"\u002Fcrypto\u002Fmetodologiya-yldx-upravlenie-riskom","Риск в DeFi — не лотерея, а математика: методология YLDX","В 2022 году из DeFi украли $3.2 млрд — почти 6% всего рынка. Но риск в пуле ликвидности можно посчитать заранее и разложить так, что провал одного пула превращается из катастрофы в царапину. Разбираем методологию, по которой фонд YLDX выбирает пулы, делит капитал и ограничивает потери.","Редакция","2026-07-13","\u002Fcovers\u002Fyldx-risk.svg",5,{"_path":355,"title":356,"lead":357,"rubric":5,"author":350,"date":358,"cover":359,"readingTime":326},"\u002Fcrypto\u002Fsamostoyatelnoe-hranenie","«Не твои ключи — не твои монеты»: как на самом деле работает самостоятельное хранение","Криптовалюта не лежит в кошельке — она записана в блокчейне. Кошелёк хранит только ключ. Разбираем, что это значит на практике и почему одна ошибка при копировании адреса может стоить всех денег.","2026-07-08","\u002Fcovers\u002Fself-custody.svg",{"_path":361,"title":362,"lead":363,"rubric":5,"author":350,"date":364,"cover":365,"readingTime":326},"\u002Fcrypto\u002Flikvidnost-prostymi-slovami","Ликвидность простыми словами: почему в DeFi она решает всё","Пулы ликвидности заменили биржевой стакан математической формулой. Объясняем, как работает автоматический маркетмейкер, откуда берётся доходность поставщиков ликвидности и за что они на самом деле получают комиссию.","2026-06-28","\u002Fcovers\u002Fliquidity.svg",1784261629054]